    "is_free": false,
    "description": "Travel back in time and explore historically accurate ancient cities in this family-friendly action-adventure RPG. Meet real scientists who changed the world, battle monsters to protect the future, and solve puzzles while defeating bosses in this story-rich 2D adventure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Story</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/259a2ec28907f7983601ebaf9ccfd174.poster.avif?t=1721237926\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/259a2ec28907f7983601ebaf9ccfd174.webm?t=1721237926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/259a2ec28907f7983601ebaf9ccfd174.mp4?t=1721237926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It’s 2050 and your first day at the astounding Aqli Academy for Gifted Children where you’ll meet your new brainiac buddies Khalid, Layla, Abdullah, and Aysha.<br><br>They need <strong>YOUR</strong> help investigating a mysterious machine that unexpectedly unleashes a crash course in history!<br><br>But watch out, there are dastardly, diabolical villains trying to change the course of time and the fate of history is at stake! The Time Hoppers will need to stop the machinations of the mad alchemist, Dr. Fasid, and his maniacal minions!<br><br>The Time Hoppers are prepared with technological tools and futuristic techniques to overcome whatever they encounter! Wander across wild desert wastes and whimsical cities in the wondrous ancient worlds waiting for you! Curiosity is richly rewarded with troves of treasure and nuggets of knowledge.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Travel to Save Scientists</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/f64a2431e6c4c83790ee8932bffb91a7.poster.avif?t=1721237926\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/f64a2431e6c4c83790ee8932bffb91a7.webm?t=1721237926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/f64a2431e6c4c83790ee8932bffb91a7.mp4?t=1721237926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Meet real scientists who changed the world and complete quests to protect their inventions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/536d687301f9afd59df70886ae5740a9.poster.avif?t=1721237926\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/536d687301f9afd59df70886ae5740a9.webm?t=1721237926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/536d687301f9afd59df70886ae5740a9.mp4?t=1721237926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You’ll be hopping back in time from the 7th to 15th century and adventuring across 7 lovingly recreated locales along the Silk Road!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight Monsters</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/5a92f8fbbe895cb458fab1d810662245.poster.avif?t=1721237926\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/5a92f8fbbe895cb458fab1d810662245.webm?t=1721237926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/5a92f8fbbe895cb458fab1d810662245.mp4?t=1721237926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your Nano Blaster to fight off armies of abnormal alchemical abominations.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Puzzles</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/24462c3ba8031c109a7f7e8d111d9aa3.poster.avif?t=1721237926\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/24462c3ba8031c109a7f7e8d111d9aa3.webm?t=1721237926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283660/extras/24462c3ba8031c109a7f7e8d111d9aa3.mp4?t=1721237926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your mind to solve puzzles to progress through a rich story.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Learn real ancient knowledge from real historical figures while bamboozling bad guys and abnormal alchemical abominations.<br></li><li>Packed full of peculiar puzzles, creative challenges, quirky quests, and minigames so you have non-stop new stuff to do!<br></li><li>Your skills and wits will be put to the test to uncover the treacherous tale of Dr. Fasid’s terrifying timeline!<br></li><li>Show off some of your special spoils in your customizable base back at the Academy!<br></li><li>Fully voice acted to bring the colorful collection of characters to life! Younger Hoppers can follow along easily too!<br></li><li>Comic-style cutscenes expand on exciting moments!<br></li><li>Adorable, hand-crafted aesthetic is optimized to run silky-smooth, even on low-end hardware.</li></ul>",
